Hello Everyone! To round out the last week of Women's History Month, we have some exciting industry office hours planned this week. Everyone is welcome to join and we will be raffling off some prizes to attendees. Prizes include Google Home Mini, Google swag bag, Amazon Prime subscription, Fujifilm camera, EECS swag and more!

Monday 3/29

Pinecone OH: https://tinyurl.com/pinecone-oh 5-6pm PT

Tuesday 3/30

Google OH: RSVP here https://bit.ly/3vQuGbf

Link: meet.google.com/pcj-tbua-szm 10-11am PT

Databricks OH: RSVP here

Link: Databricks OH Zoom Link 5-6pm PT

Wednesday 3/31

General Motors OH:  Zoom Link Here 4-5pm PT

SAP Women In Tech Panel: https://tinyurl.com/sap-panel 5-6pm PT

View our full calendar here https://www.eecswhm.com/

Join our discord to ask any other questions! https://tinyurl.com/eecswhm2021
